<template><div><section class="print-section">
<h1 id="data-science-—-final-exam-answer-sheet-solutions" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#data-science-—-final-exam-answer-sheet-solutions"><span>Data Science — Final Exam: Answer Sheet &amp; Solutions</span></a></h1>
