<h3 id="c-new-centroids-and-assignment-of-p-3-3" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#c-new-centroids-and-assignment-of-p-3-3"><span>(c) New Centroids and Assignment of p = (3, 3)</span></a></h3>
