<section class="print-section">
<h3 id="f-five-inter-cluster-linkage-methods" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#f-five-inter-cluster-linkage-methods"><span>(f) Five Inter-Cluster Linkage Methods</span></a></h3>
